Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バシサイヨ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ナイダ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青辣椒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:47.57,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,436)}<Jalapeno>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有著這樣的過去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再 再怎麼說也太...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 姐姐大人 這肯定是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我熟人的朋友也是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 都寫在網上了 肯定是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於Sleeping啥的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面說美國大兵做寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 是防衛過當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:20.84,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧～對吧～對吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好好好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:25.81,*title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(200,10)}10cm的距離是有意義的！你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃紫葉醬菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:38.28,*title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(345,10)\fs19}看了下久違的原neta 原來當時腮幫子那麼大啊 {\1c&H4D81DF}不過年輕的時候 完全沒放在心上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從上述的事情上看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學園都市進行的能力開發課程當中
